title: Pixel 3XL battery drain after update to Android 10, "-5" mysterious app
content:
My battery performance has dropped significantly and the only thing I can point to is an app called "-5". I try to open it and Google photos opens. I try to uninstall and I get kicked back to the battery screen. No minutes used, no background. 

What is this??
category: Battery and Power, Google Pixel 3 XL
